The '''''Vigilant''''' was a [[Majestic-class heavy cruiser|''Majestic''-class heavy cruiser]] that saw service within the [[New Republic Fifth Fleet|Fifth Battle Group]] of the [[New Republic Defense Force/Legends|New Republic Defense Force]] in [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]]. The warship participated in the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic's]] campaign against the [[Duskhan League]] during the [[Black Fleet Crisis]].

